{"tid":2066944,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［搵歷史學家］呢本野係BNO前身？？","createTime":"2020-06-16T15:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T05:17:00.000Z","uid":326930,"like":9,"dislike":93,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"cc76b77905bfe8ad32e5d2b02f67c5898e015aed","tid":2066944,"uid":326930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:41:35.000Z","msg":"唔知po咩台。。。<br />\n萬一po錯，跪求插細力啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先出幾張相：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y94KmeW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY94KmeW.jpg&h=d34745e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c5hoBOe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc5hoBOe.jpg&h=51498d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BhMMzzT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBhMMzzT.jpg&h=4703cd67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hU1D98c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhU1D98c.jpg&h=48e9ddc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，<br />\n家人於1974年時曾經出國，<br />\n申請左果個年代既「護照」，<br />\n後來就一路都無再離開過HK<br />\n<br />\n以致呢本野變左唯一，<br />\n後來既BNO、特衰護照都無申請到。<br />\n<br />\n請問一下全能的連登仔囡，<br />\n呢本野既持有人，<br />\n今時今日，是否仍擁有BNO既申請資格？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97034db9df3ea861ec3b27e05bb1c677cf6eeee5","tid":2066944,"uid":40317,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:44:10.000Z","msg":"我屋企人都有呢本嘢。。。我都想知"},{"pid":"3b44015545d137967dd5b22067215b2f50101b01","tid":2066944,"uid":326930,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"97034db9df3ea861ec3b27e05bb1c677cf6eeee5","tid":2066944,"uid":40317,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:44:10.000Z","msg":"我屋企人都有呢本嘢。。。我都想知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T15:53:43.000Z","msg":"我推唔到，靠你得閒幫推幾下啦 <img s